---
title: Smoky Stuffed Mushrooms with Tomato Quinoa and Cheesy Breadcrumbs
description: Had enough of quinoa yet? Good, neither have we. We’re happy to explore each and every way that you can use the protein-rich seed. Next up: stuffed portobellos. Both the quinoa filling and mushrooms are seasoned with warm spices, giving you waves of smokiness, savoriness, and mild heat in each bite. Everything gets sprinkled with a mozzarella and panko breadcrumb garnish, so there’s plenty of crunch and cheesy goodness to go around, too.
